headline: HF FOODS GROUP INC. (HFFG) Surpasses Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: HF FOODS GROUP (HFFG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 22.22% and 6.05%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
